  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">STAR 2 - #STOPGALAMSEY</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.	A reduction in illegal mining activities;
2.	Reclamation of sites otherwise ravaged by illegal mining activities;
3.	A remarkable improvement in the quality of waterbodies destroyed and polluted by illegal mining activities; and
4.	A sustainable system of small scale mining for the people otherwise involved in illegal mining activities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A.	Major and coordinated media attention on the activities of small scale mining
B.	Stakeholder engagements with relevant organisations involved in mining, research, education, health, etc.;
C.	Town hall meetings across the country to draw attention of people living in the communities of the direct effect of galamsey on their livelihood; 
D.	National fora to gather/formulate solutions to the menace of illegal mining;
E.	Collection of at least 1 million signatures in support of a petition to be delivered to H. E. the President of Ghana, the Speaker of Parliament and the Chief Justice; and 
F.	Organized manifestations of our abhorrence of the mining illegalities such as declaring &#x201C;Red Fridays&#x201D; on the last Friday of every month.</narrative>
  </description>
